@base = http://localhost:7331

### Health check — all UP (→ 200)
GET {{base}}/health

### Simulate cache failure
POST {{base}}/demo/cache/down

### Health check — cache DOWN (→ 503)
GET {{base}}/health

### Restore cache
POST {{base}}/demo/cache/up

### Simulate database failure
POST {{base}}/demo/database/down

### Health check — database DOWN (→ 503)
GET {{base}}/health

### Restore database
POST {{base}}/demo/database/up

### Health check — all restored (→ 200)
GET {{base}}/health
